node

Interface NodeInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Fold, InverseSurrogateFold, InverseSurrogateNeighbor, Neighbor, Node, NodeRole, SurrogateFold, SurrogateNeighbor

    public interface NodeInterface
    All of the methods as defined by the Node specification. Additionally, the addMe(), disconnectMe(), and replaceMe(Node) methods have been added.
    Author:
    Craig Jacobson
